        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[疑问]#哪些原因会导致呼吸道不适#】专家介绍，慢性疾病与流行性感冒都会引起呼吸道不适，而肺部有基础性疾病的人群，冬季受凉会引起咳嗽加重。#不同情况引起...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些原因会导致呼吸道不适#</span></a>】专家介绍，慢性疾病与流行性感冒都会引起呼吸道不适，而肺部有基础性疾病的人群，冬季受凉会引起咳嗽加重。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不同情况引起的咳嗽症状不同#</span></a>，①慢性支气管炎：咳嗽咳泡沫样痰，连续2年以上；②支气管哮喘：反复发作、伴咳嗽咳痰，过敏原诱发；③支气管扩张：持续反复，咳黄脓痰，痰中带血。以上三类人群，冬季要注意防范🥶👇🏻（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6lxR0te" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
